<item>
 <title>Prototyping excellence: a Design+Content-first approach to websites</title>
 <link>http://badcamp-2015.kbox/session/prototyping-excellence-designcontent-first-approach-websites</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-youtube field-type-youtube field-label-hidden field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe id=&quot;youtube-field-player&quot; class=&quot;youtube-field-player&quot;
    width=&quot;420&quot; height=&quot;315&quot;
    src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/F2t03HAKuok?modestbranding=1&amp;wmode=opaque&quot; title=&quot;Embedded video for Prototyping excellence: a Design+Content-first approach to websites&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot;
    allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;body field&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://nyccamp.org/sites/default/files/images/sessions/Kalastatic_1.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prototype clean, beautiful sites that users enjoy and clients can easily collaborate on and understand. We’ll introduce &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/kalamuna/kalastatic&quot;&gt;kalastatic&lt;/a&gt;, the open-source Kalamuna prototyping tool that co-exists with Drupal themes, Wordpress, and stand-alone sites, and consumes JSON from Drupal 7, 8 or other services. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A solid prototyping framework should put in practice &lt;a href=&quot;http://bradfrost.com/blog/post/atomic-web-design&quot;&gt;atomic web design&lt;/a&gt; principles to produce a &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.webdesignerdepot.com/2014/09/how-to-make-your-code-easily-maintainable-with-living-style-guides&quot;&gt;living styleguide&lt;/a&gt; to guide back-end implementations in a framework agnostic approach. It should serve as a point of convergence between front-end development, back-end development, and content strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BENEFITS TO THIS APPROACH&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Enable designers and front-end developers to focus on their craft instead of struggling with poorly documented CMS APIs and configurations.&lt;br /&gt;
	 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive design thinking early in the project lifecycle by giving clients something they can see and understand.&lt;br /&gt;
	 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide a litmus test against style regressions during development by using the prototype as a living style guide.&lt;br /&gt;
	 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accelerate development by using a workspace for front-to-back and back-to-front collaboration.&lt;br /&gt;
	 &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft small sites with fun and fury, not tedium and infinite clicks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-track field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session track: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/tracks/design-theme-ux&quot;&gt;Design, Theme + UX&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-skill-level field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session skill level: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/skill-level/intermediate&quot;&gt;Intermediate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-speaker field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textformatter-list&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/andrewmallis&quot; class=&quot;user user-25 entityreference&quot;&gt;Andrew_Mallis&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/users/robloach&quot; class=&quot;user user-958 entityreference&quot;&gt;RobLoach&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-date-and-time field-type-datetime field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session date and time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;date-display-single&quot;&gt;Saturday, October 24, 2015 - 4:30pm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-time-slot field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session time slot: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/time-slot/430pm-500pm&quot;&gt;4:30pm - 5:00pm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-room field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session room: &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;links inline&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;taxonomy-term-reference-0&quot; class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/rooms/stephens-lounge-usc-student-union-building-0&quot;&gt;Stephens Lounge - USC Student Union Building&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-session-files field-type-file field-label-inline clearfix field-wrapper&quot;&gt;&lt;div  class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Session files:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;file-icon&quot; alt=&quot;PDF icon&quot; title=&quot;application/pdf&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://badcamp-2015.kbox/sites/default/files/session-files/kalastatic%E2%80%93badcamp2015.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=3419453&quot;&gt;kalastatic–badcamp2015.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
